%% Diagram: Supply Chain Attestation
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  participant CI as CI runner
  participant OIDC as CI OIDC issuer
  participant Fulcio
  participant Rekor
  participant Reg as OCI registry
  participant Adm as Admission controller
  CI->>OIDC: 1. Request workflow id token
  OIDC-->>CI: 2. Signed JWT (workflow identity)
  CI->>Fulcio: 3. Exchange JWT for short-lived cert
  Fulcio-->>CI: 4. X.509 cert bound to identity
  CI->>CI: 5. Build image, compute digest
  CI->>CI: 6. Generate SLSA provenance and SBOM
  CI->>Rekor: 7. Log signature and attestation
  Rekor-->>CI: 8. Inclusion proof
  CI->>Reg: 9. Push image + signature + in-toto attestations
  Note over Reg: Image addressed by digest, not tag
  Adm->>Reg: 10. Pull image and attestations at deploy
  Adm->>Adm: 11. cosign verify (identity + issuer + predicate)
  Adm-->>Reg: 12. Admit only if policy passes
